Kevin Neil Whitrick
{{an hero}}

'''Kevin Whitrick''' (1965 - 3/23/2007) caused much [[Internet drama]] and became [[an hero]] after hanging himself...live on webcam. Apparently, Mr. Whitrick from Wellington, Telford, Shropshire, [[England]] had [[butthurt|chronic depression]], so the best course of action for him was to be a camwhore. In the spirit of [[Ripper|Brandon Vedas]], he too wanted to prove he was hardcore, and went into a chatroom full of spiteful trolls on Paltalk. He claimed he wanted to [[permaban]] himself from life, and other users egged him on. One member (in true English style) went as far as to say:

{{quote|Fucking do it, get on with it! Get it round your neck. For fuck's sake...he can't even do this properly!}}

