==In Memoriam==

Kevin Neil Whitrick was a true pioneer, a man with a vision. Whitrick was to webcam broadcasts what [[Budd Dwyer]] was to televised press conferences. Brandon Vedas aside, Whitrick was the first man to intentionally [[self-pwn]] on streaming webcam. It is to this man and his genius that this page is dedicated. 

{{quote|Southern trees bear strange fruit,
Blood on the leaves and blood at the root,
White body swinging in the southern breeze,
Strange fruit hanging from the poplar trees.

Pastoral scene of the gallant south,
The bulging eyes and the twisted mouth,
Scent of magnolias, sweet and fresh,
Then the sudden smell of burning flesh.

Here is fruit for the crows to pluck,
For the rain to gather, for the wind to suck,
For the sun to rot, for the trees to drop,
Here is a strange and bitter crop|Lemmy Kilmister, Motorhead}}

Inevitably, what the white man has, the [[CandyJunkie|black man]] taketh away.

